  <p><strong>Years:</strong> 1925, 1937, 1949, 1961, 1973, 1985, 1997, 2009, 2021, 2033</p>
  <p><strong>Element:</strong> Earth &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Polarity:</strong> Yin &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Hours:</strong> 01:00&ndash;03:00 &nbsp;|&nbsp; <strong>Direction:</strong> North-northeast</p>
  <p>The <a href="/zodiac/ox/">Ox</a> is the embodiment of <strong>diligence, patience, and quiet strength</strong>. Where the Rat wins through cunning, the Ox succeeds through sheer persistence. Ox people are the dependable foundations of families, organisations, and communities &mdash; they carry burdens without complaint and finish what they start.</p>
  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong> Reliability, determination, methodical thinking, integrity, physical endurance.</p>
  <p><strong>Challenges:</strong> Stubbornness, resistance to change, difficulty expressing emotions, possessiveness.</p>
</section>
