  <p><strong>Strengths:</strong> Ambition, confidence, vitality, generosity, visionary thinking.</p>
  <p><strong>Challenges:</strong> Arrogance, impatience with mediocrity, difficulty accepting criticism, burnout from overcommitment.</p>
